\mt2 Moęž‰foęž‰s We Foęž‰l Eyoęž‰  
\mt1 Galasia  
\mt2 Kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰ Saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰  
\imt1 Asulumaęž‰noęž‰ towoęž‰ we  
\ip Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ to nafa widaęž‰li haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, Galasia saęž‰soęž‰ aęž‰na moęž‰moęž‰doęž‰. Tif amioęž‰ Yu widan kalu nowoęž‰ aęž‰na haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ aęž‰widakiyoęž‰, â€śGioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ digaloęž‰ domaęž‰nikiyoęž‰, Moęž‰saęž‰saęž‰ ele saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ mada kudu haęž‰naęž‰biâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰widoęž‰. Galasia tilidabu kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ halayoęž‰ moęž‰asulumaęž‰ki, Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ asuloęž‰ dimiakiyoęž‰, moęž‰foęž‰s we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰.  
\ip Moęž‰foęž‰s us wenamioęž‰, Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰lakiyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰, â€śGioęž‰ Yaęž‰su amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab aęž‰namioęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ si waęž‰l amioęž‰ digaloęž‰le faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ibâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Foęž‰l e iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu nowoęž‰ eloęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰samaęž‰kiyoęž‰, imoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰soęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰, â€śTo we ni asuloęž‰ amiloęž‰woęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰ba. Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ nemoęž‰loęž‰ fanda widoęž‰ aumboęž‰ gimoęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰lâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰.  
\ip Foęž‰l eloęž‰ to saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ nowoęž‰ we. Nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ digaloęž‰le domaęž‰nikiyoęž‰, nili tilidabu aęž‰maęž‰ ilikiyoęž‰, digaloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰do alifaęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Yaęž‰su eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ gaęž‰li sili alitaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, ene Mama eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ tililiaęž‰ haęž‰nabiki, nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ enedoęž‰ asulab man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Ne Foęž‰l, iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu nowoęž‰ ne. Ne nanog dimaęž‰kiyoęž‰, kaluwaęž‰ halaidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ daęž‰feaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ iligaęž‰foma. Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰ Do Gode, Yaęž‰su sowoęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ dasi alifaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ne ene nanog aęž‰noęž‰ dimaęž‰ki daęž‰feaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ iligaęž‰foęž‰.  
\v 2 Moęž‰foęž‰s we ne oęž‰liaęž‰ Keliso kalukaęž‰isale wiloęž‰ sab niliyoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, saęž‰s tambo Galasia hen aęž‰namiloęž‰ aęž‰lab gimoęž‰ iligaęž‰toęž‰l.   
\p
\v 3 Nili Do Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ Alan Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, haęž‰sa mesaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ domaęž‰ki dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1.4 \xt Gala 2.20\x*Yaęž‰su eyoęž‰ nili Do Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab au kudu haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, nili mogagoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ halaęž‰maęž‰ki, ene melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰kanulaki dimi. Nioęž‰ henfeloęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ usamiloęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ sili alifomaęž‰ki, Yaęž‰su eyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidoęž‰.  
\v 5 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ niliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ wiyoęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo wabudaęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰. Hendele.   
\s1 To nafa hendeyoęž‰ imilig koęž‰loęž‰lab  
\p
\v 6 Amayoęž‰! Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰namioęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale gioęž‰ enoęž‰le domaęž‰ki hoęž‰idoęž‰ koęž‰sega, giliyoęž‰ kalu giloęž‰ hoęž‰idoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ boęž‰boęž‰ge gola baęž‰dakiyoęž‰, to koęž‰li widab aęž‰noęž‰ kudu haęž‰nait koęž‰loęž‰ ne mada iligoęž‰.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1.7 \xt Ilig 15.1,24\x*To koęž‰li aęž‰widab ko, to nafaleyoęž‰ oęž‰mba. Kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰li nodo saęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ babale asulumaęž‰ki gab.   
\p
\v 8 \x - \xo 1.8 \xt 1Kol 16.22\x*Koęž‰sega toloęž‰ widan kalu niyaęž‰le, maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalu Hebene aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ yab aęž‰maęž‰yaęž‰le, to nafa koęž‰loęž‰ niloęž‰ tamin amiloęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ nodolaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, gimoęž‰woęž‰ to koęž‰li aęž‰widalega, Gode eyoęž‰ kalu i aęž‰noęž‰ waęž‰deaki, de hena melaęž‰noęž‰ meleaęž‰ki asulab.  
\v 9 To nafa aęž‰noęž‰ niyoęž‰ sioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ waęž‰ka saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. Kalu abeyoęž‰ to nafa gililoęž‰ tamin amiloęž‰ tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ nodolaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, gimoęž‰woęž‰ to koęž‰li aęž‰widalega, Gode eyoęž‰ kalu aęž‰noęž‰ waęž‰deaki de hena melaęž‰noęž‰ meseaęž‰ki asulab.   
\p
\v 10 \x - \xo 1.10 \xt 1Tes 2.4\x*To we niyoęž‰ widakiyoęž‰, kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰yoęž‰ nemoęž‰ sagalemaęž‰ki widoęž‰lba. Gode eyoęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ sagalemaęž‰ki widoęž‰l. Niyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale koęž‰loęž‰ sagalemaęž‰ki widai kiboęž‰bowoęž‰, ne Kelisowaęž‰ nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu hendeleyoęž‰ moęž‰domoęž‰lo.   
\s1 Foęž‰l e iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu domaęž‰ki Godeyaęž‰ hoęž‰idoęž‰  
\p
\v 11 \x - \xo 1.11 \xt Madi 16.17\x*Ni nao nado i, gioęž‰ fanda asulumaęž‰ki soęž‰loęž‰l. Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ to nafale koęž‰loęž‰ niloęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ kaluwaęž‰ asuloęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ mioęž‰ma.  
\v 12 Niyoęž‰ to we nili maęž‰muwaęž‰ man aęž‰namiloęž‰ moęž‰di aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰widoęž‰. Oęž‰ngoęž‰ma. To nafa we Yaęž‰su Kelisowoęž‰ neloęž‰wa faęž‰laęž‰dowaki, nemoęž‰woęž‰ kalaba widoęž‰.   
\p
\v 13 \x - \xo 1.13 \xt Ilig 8.3\x*Yuwaęž‰ ele kudu haęž‰naęž‰likiloęž‰ man niloęž‰ dimidan aęž‰noęž‰ gioęž‰ tamin amioęž‰ dabu. Niyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene saęž‰s kalukaęž‰isale oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ dimiaki, tambo yasa danelaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ asulaki dimidaęž‰len.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1.14 \xt Ilig 22.3\x*Nili maęž‰muwaęž‰ ele difaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ne mada halaidoęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰len. Yuwaęž‰ ele man aęž‰noęž‰ asululiaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰likiyoęž‰, niasi kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ ne tinioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ elen.  
\v 15-16 \x - \xo 1.15-16 \xt Ais 49.1, Gala 2.7\x*Koęž‰sega, ne oęž‰saęž‰laęž‰liaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ nemoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lakiyoęž‰, ene nanog dimaęž‰ki daęž‰feyoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ niyoęž‰ to nafa Yu kalukaęž‰isalema imoęž‰woęž‰ walamaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene insoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwoęž‰ nemoęž‰ widoęž‰. Hoęž‰len nemoęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰ amioęž‰, ne kalu no oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ nenelemaęž‰nikiyoęž‰ moęž‰ane.  
\v 17 Hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ tamin amiloęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ Yaęž‰lusalem elen koęž‰sega, niyoęž‰ iyoęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰baęž‰baęž‰ni ane. Ne Alabia hen aęž‰naka tigini haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, tif amioęž‰ Damaskas amisaęž‰na aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ mioęž‰.   
\p
\v 18 \x - \xo 1.18 \xt Ilig 9.26-27\x*Dona otalenoęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, ne Bidayoęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰niki, Yaęž‰lusalemoęž‰ aęž‰na ane. Ne Bida oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ senoęž‰, hoęž‰lenoęž‰ doęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ bilaęž‰foęž‰ dowoęž‰.  
\v 19 Ne Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ ene ao, Yaęž‰maęž‰s koęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰ koęž‰sega, iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu nol aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰baęž‰baęž‰.  
\v 20 To niloęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰l we hendele aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰la soęž‰loęž‰l.   
\p
\v 21 \x - \xo 1.21 \xt Ilig 9.30\x*Ne Yaęž‰lusalem aęž‰na saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Silia hena aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Silisia hen aęž‰namidaęž‰ ane.  
\v 22 Hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, saęž‰s kalukaęž‰isale Yudia hen amiloęž‰ sab i aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ne semoęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 23 Koęž‰sega iliyoęž‰ niloęž‰ dimidaęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ malolabiki aęž‰laęž‰dabu, â€śTamin amiloęž‰ Keliso kalukaęž‰isale niloęž‰ mogagilaęž‰sen kalu aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ to eloęž‰ mogagilaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰ e widaęž‰labâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰maloloęž‰ meabiki dabuloęž‰bo.  
\v 24 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ nemoęž‰loęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, iliyoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ wabulu sioęž‰.   
\c 2  
\s1 Iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ Foęž‰l e oęž‰likaęž‰ aęž‰lakiyoęž‰ daęž‰fe alifaęž‰  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 2.1 \xt Ilig 15.2\x*Donayoęž‰ doęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰daęž‰in aęž‰noęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, ne Yaęž‰lusalemoęž‰ waęž‰ka haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, Banabasoęž‰ ne oęž‰liaęž‰ ane. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Taitusoęž‰loęž‰ tililiaęž‰gane.  
\v 2 Gode eyoęž‰ ne Yaęž‰lusalem aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ hamanaęž‰ki widoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ ne aęž‰na ane. Niloęž‰ Yu kaluma oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ nanog tamin amiloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ oęž‰gdoęž‰ dimidaęž‰loęž‰l aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ madali walaęž‰maęž‰kiyoęž‰ moęž‰asuloęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ne aęž‰na haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan misaęž‰ kalu egelese silikiyoęž‰, niyoęž‰ towoęž‰ Yu kalukaęž‰isalema imoęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ misaęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ fanda asulumaęž‰ki maloloęž‰ me.  
\v 3 Taitus ne oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ mioęž‰ e Gilig kalu, koęž‰sega iliyoęž‰ to niloęž‰ sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, e doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedema aęž‰lakiyoęž‰ iliyoęž‰ moęž‰dibodoęž‰.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2.4 \xt Gala 1.7, 5.1,13\x*Koęž‰sega kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ Taitusoęž‰ doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedemaęž‰ki asuloęž‰. Kalu i aęž‰noęž‰ tilidabu kalu hendelema. Iyoęž‰ nililoęž‰ nenelab us aęž‰na kaęž‰laęž‰gedemaęž‰ni yakiyoęž‰, nililoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso amiloęž‰ gaęž‰liloęž‰ dowab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, boęž‰boęž‰le baęž‰baęž‰ni mioęž‰. I aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ dibolo taęž‰faęž‰niki, Yuwaęž‰ ele haęž‰ga dowaki, madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu oęž‰ngoęž‰ domaęž‰ki asuloęž‰.  
\v 5 Koęž‰sega niliyoęž‰ ililoęž‰ asulab aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰lakiyoęž‰, to imilig gedeaęž‰taki, moęž‰kudu ane. To nafa hendele aęž‰noęž‰ giya dofoęž‰meleaęž‰kiyoęž‰, niliyoęž‰ ililoęž‰ asulab aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰g amioęž‰ moęž‰dowoęž‰.  
\v 6 Koęž‰sega Yaęž‰lusalem saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan misaęž‰ kalu i aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ to niloęž‰ sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ modaęž‰daęž‰li silikiyoęž‰, iliyoęž‰ towoęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰kudu sioęž‰. Gode eyoęž‰ kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰ waęž‰l wenamiloęž‰ nili siyaęž‰loęž‰ baęž‰dab aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰alobaęž‰daęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, niyoęž‰loęž‰ wiloęž‰ di kaluloęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰molo asuloęž‰l.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2.7 \xt Ilig 22.21\x*Saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan misaęž‰ kalu iliyoęž‰ to nowoęž‰ moęž‰kudu saęž‰lai koęž‰sega, ili asulakiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ Bidayoęž‰ Yu kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰loęž‰ to walamaęž‰kiloęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, neloęž‰ Yu kalukaęž‰isalema imoęž‰woęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ walamaęž‰ki daęž‰feyoęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ iliyoęž‰ asuloęž‰.  
\v 8 Bidayoęž‰ Yu kalukaęž‰isale us aęž‰na nanogdoęž‰ dimidabikiloęž‰, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ e asufaęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, neloęž‰ Yu kalukaęž‰isalema us aęž‰na nanogoęž‰ dimidaęž‰likiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ ne aęž‰na asufaęž‰.  
\v 9 Saęž‰s amiloęž‰ misaęž‰ kalu saboęž‰, Yaęž‰maęž‰soęž‰, Bidayoęž‰, Yoęž‰noęž‰, i aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, kalu otalen aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ ne oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laki, nanog aęž‰noęž‰ nemoęž‰ dimiloęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, nioęž‰ to imilise diaęž‰taki, Banabas naęž‰n oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ dagiyoęž‰ ebeyoęž‰. Naęž‰noęž‰ Yu kalukaęž‰isalema imoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ widaęž‰b, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iliyoęž‰loęž‰ Yu kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ widaęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰, negeleboęž‰ towoęž‰ saefaęž‰.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2.10 \xt Ilig 11.29-30\x*Iliyoęž‰ naęž‰nboęž‰woęž‰ dabu baęž‰dakiyoęž‰, Yu amiloęž‰ tilidabu kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asuwaęž‰foma aęž‰laęž‰liki dabu baęž‰baęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to aęž‰namioęž‰ niloęž‰ tamin amiloęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ asululiyoęž‰ oęž‰m.   
\s1 Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Bidamoęž‰woęž‰ towoęž‰ tigini sioęž‰  
\p
\v 11 Koęž‰sega tif amioęž‰, Bidayoęž‰ Antioęž‰g amisaęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ sabikiyoęž‰, e halayoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, niyoęž‰ emoęž‰woęž‰ tigini sioęž‰.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 2.12 \xt Ilig 11.3\x*Bida eloęž‰ hala dimidoęž‰woęž‰ we. Bida e hoęž‰gi faęž‰laęž‰dowakiyoęž‰, Yuma tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale i oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ uwa naęž‰len. Koęž‰sega Yu kalu nol, Yaęž‰maęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ iligaęž‰foęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowabikiyoęž‰, Bida e Yuma kalukaęž‰isale i oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰gasa dowaki, maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ waęž‰kabiyoęž‰ moęž‰moęž‰noęž‰. Moęž‰woęž‰ kalu nolbaęž‰loęž‰ â€śkalu doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ moęž‰hege gedealega, e Kelisowoęž‰ moęž‰domaęž‰ibâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lan aęž‰noęž‰ asulaki, Bida e aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ tagilaki elen.  
\v 13 Bida eyoęž‰ digaloęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ asulufoęž‰liki koęž‰sega, e kalu nol aęž‰noęž‰ tagilaki, manoęž‰ koęž‰li dimidoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Yu tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale Antioęž‰gdoęž‰ san iliyoęž‰loęž‰ eloęž‰ man dimidab aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ kudu ane koęž‰loęž‰, man ililoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Banabas e sendeliaęž‰gane koęž‰loęž‰ eloęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ka dimidoęž‰.   
\p
\v 14 Ne baęž‰baęž‰ amioęž‰ ililoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ to nafa hendele oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰imiloęž‰ dowoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asulab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale tambo dabumaęž‰kiyoęž‰, niyoęž‰ Bidamoęž‰woęž‰ tigini saęž‰laki aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰, â€śGe Yu kalu, koęž‰sega Yuwaęž‰ eleyoęž‰ tambo moęž‰kudu haęž‰naki, Yu kaluma ili man oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ge kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ giloęž‰ Yu kalukaęž‰isalema koęž‰loęž‰ Yuwaęž‰ ele aęž‰noęž‰ kudu hamanaęž‰kiloęž‰ dibodab ko, moęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰?   
\p
\v 15 â€śNili maęž‰mu iyoęž‰ Yu kalu koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰liab amioęž‰ Yu kalule dowoęž‰. Yu kaluma i aęž‰noęž‰ mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidan kalu aęž‰laęž‰soęž‰loęž‰l koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ kalu i oęž‰ngoęž‰ma.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 2.16 \xt Ilig 15.10-11, Lom 3.20-28, Gala 3.11\x*Koęž‰sega niliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰l. Kalukaęž‰isale Moęž‰saęž‰saęž‰ eleloęž‰ tambo kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, kalu we digaloęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰saęž‰lan. Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ moęž‰aumaęž‰ib. Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab aęž‰noęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ e digaloęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰maęž‰ib. Yu kalu, Yaęž‰su amiloęž‰ tilidabu niliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ asulufoęž‰loęž‰l. Hendele nioęž‰loęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ digaloęž‰ kalu aęž‰laęž‰samaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Yaęž‰su Keliso e amioęž‰ tilidabu. Eleloęž‰ kudu haęž‰nab aęž‰namioęž‰ nioęž‰ digaloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ moęž‰saęž‰maęž‰ib. Moęž‰woęž‰ ele koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kalu imilig nowoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ digaloęž‰woęž‰ mada moęž‰taęž‰faęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 17 â€śOęž‰goęž‰ niliyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰baęž‰noęž‰ man kudu haęž‰nab aęž‰namioęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ digaloęž‰le aęž‰laęž‰asulab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ niliyoęž‰ tog aęž‰na iliki baęž‰baęž‰ amioęž‰, nioęž‰loęž‰ mogagoęž‰ kalule dowab aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰ koęž‰sega Kelisowaęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ mogagoęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰li ka dimidamaęž‰ki saęž‰laigabaęž‰le? Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ moęž‰aumaęž‰ib!  
\v 18 Tamin amiloęž‰ ele kudu haęž‰nan man koęž‰loęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ niyoęž‰ waęž‰ka aęž‰tili daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ kudu haęž‰nalega, mogagoęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ ne, aęž‰laęž‰liki widakigab.  
\v 19 Tamin amioęž‰ neloęž‰ ele aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰ga elen koęž‰sega aęž‰namiloęž‰ elenoęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ handalowoęž‰ amioęž‰, ne Gode enoęž‰le dowaki, e kudu haęž‰naęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 2.20 \xt Gala 1.4\x*Ne Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰ i malana sowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, melaęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰gi di aęž‰noęž‰ ninoęž‰ma. Ne amioęž‰ Keliso e melaęž‰noęž‰ sab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ne henfeloęž‰ wena silikiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene Soęž‰waya tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰. Moęž‰woęž‰ eyoęž‰ ne mada alan asulakiyoęž‰ ene melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ neya walaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 21 Gode eyoęž‰ ne haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lakiyoęž‰, ne digaloęž‰ kalu aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ ne oęž‰ngoęž‰maloęž‰ngoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰asulumaęž‰noęž‰. Kalukaęž‰isale imilig nowoęž‰ ele mada kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab aęž‰namioęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ nafa digaloęž‰ ka dowan kibabeyoęž‰, Yaęž‰su Keliso sowoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰maloęž‰ngoęž‰ domabe.â€ť   
\c 3  
\s1 Tili dabu man oęž‰liaęž‰ ele kudu haęž‰nan man oęž‰liaęž‰ widoęž‰  
\p
\v 1 Galasia kalukaęž‰isale gioęž‰ asugdoęž‰ma dowab! Niliyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ kalaba widoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, e i malan amiloęž‰ alu aęž‰noęž‰ goęž‰noęž‰n siyaęž‰loęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰yoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowoęž‰. Koęž‰sega nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ dikili widoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ noęž‰nolo alifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 2 Gimoęž‰loęž‰ dabu baęž‰baęž‰nigoęž‰l we asuluma. Gioęž‰ ele kudu ane ami Godeyaęž‰ Mamayoęž‰ aęž‰na diyaęž‰le? Oęž‰ gioęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab ami Godeyaęž‰ Mamayoęž‰ aęž‰na diyaęž‰le?  
\v 3 Gioęž‰ asugdoęž‰ma dowab. Gioęž‰ moęž‰moęž‰dakiyoęž‰, Mamayaęž‰ halaidoęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ tilidabu koęž‰loęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ goęž‰noęž‰n halaidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ oęž‰li halale kagayalikiyoęž‰ egemaęž‰iba?  
\v 4 To nafa koęž‰loęž‰ gililoęž‰ kudu ane amiloęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ diaęž‰li ane aęž‰noęž‰ madali walaęž‰yaęž‰le? Niyoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ madaliloęž‰ moęž‰walaęž‰maęž‰ki asuloęž‰l.  
\v 5 Gode eyoęž‰ ene Mamayoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ dimiabikiyoęž‰, Mama aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gi usamioęž‰ molo haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ dimidoęž‰. Eloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, giyoęž‰ Yuwaęž‰ ele aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰nabiki goęž‰waęž‰le? Oęž‰ngoęž‰ma. Ginidoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso amiloęž‰ tilidabu aęž‰na goęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.   
\p
\v 6 \x - \xo 3.6 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 15.6\x*Gioęž‰ Ablahamoęž‰ asuluma. Godeyaęž‰ to saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰, â€śAblaham e Gode amioęž‰ tilidabu koęž‰loęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ e digaloęž‰ kalu aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ aęž‰na sioęž‰.â€ť  
\v 7 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ to we dinafa asuluma. Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Gode amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab aęž‰noęž‰, Ablahamaęž‰ ene insoęž‰le dowab.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 3.8 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 12.3, Lom 4.3,16\x*Gode eyoęž‰ tif amioęž‰ Yu kalukaęž‰isalema ini tilidabu amioęž‰ iyoęž‰ digaloęž‰ kalu aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰lakiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ tamina asulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Ablahamboęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dinali sioęž‰, â€śHenfeloęž‰ amiloęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰ sab aęž‰noęž‰ tambo geya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, halaidoęž‰ nafale meseaęž‰ki taęž‰faęž‰noęž‰.â€ť  
\v 9 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Ablaham e tilidaęž‰dabikiloęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ e nafale meseaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Gode amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab aęž‰noęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ i aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ nafale meseaęž‰ki taęž‰faęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 10 \x - \xo 3.10 \xt Lo 27.26\x*Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ si waęž‰l amioęž‰ Moęž‰saęž‰saęž‰ ele saefaęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰nab aęž‰namioęž‰, iyoęž‰ digaloęž‰ domaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰asulalega, Godeyaęž‰ gadioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ imoęž‰ dimiaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki dinali saefaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Godeyaęž‰ bugoęž‰ amioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰li alifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰lab, â€śKalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ ele koęž‰loęž‰ bugoęž‰ amiloęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ tambowoęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naęž‰lalega, Godeyaęž‰ gadioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ imoęž‰ dimiaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki dinali saefaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.â€ť  
\v 11 \x - \xo 3.11 \xt Hab 2.4, Gala 2.16\x*Kalu nowoęž‰ ele kudu ane aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ ge digaloęž‰lekaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ mada moęž‰saęž‰maęž‰ib. Moęž‰woęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ bugoęž‰ amioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰, â€śKalukaęž‰isale Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ digaloęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, ene tilidabu aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ene melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ dinafa tili dofoęž‰melaęž‰ib.â€ť  
\v 12 \x - \xo 3.12 \xt Wkp 18.5\x*Eleloęž‰ kudu haęž‰nan man aęž‰noęž‰ tilidabu man aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰imiloęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰ba, Godeyaęž‰ bugoęž‰ amioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰lab, â€śKalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ele saefaęž‰loęž‰ tamboloęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ e melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ diaęž‰ib.â€ť  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3.13 \xt Lo 21.23, Lom 8.3\x*Kalukaęž‰isale nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ eleyoęž‰ tambo moęž‰kudu ane koęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ gadioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ nioęž‰ diaęž‰noęž‰ elen koęž‰sega, gadioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso e diaki, nioęž‰ sili alifaęž‰. Godeyaęž‰ bugoęž‰ amioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰, â€śI malan amiloęž‰ alulab kalu aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ gadioęž‰ haęž‰g aęž‰na dowab.â€ť  
\v 14 Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ Ablahamboęž‰loęž‰ dinafa meseaęž‰kiloęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, Yu kalukaęž‰isalema iloęž‰ amioęž‰loęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Yaęž‰su e dimidoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nioęž‰ tilidaęž‰dabikiyoęž‰, Mama Maliloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ dimiaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ dimaęž‰kiyoęž‰, e dimidoęž‰.   
\s1 Ele difaęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰dilaęž‰  
\p
\v 15 Nao nado i, nili man dimidan aęž‰na daęž‰fe saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. Kalu aęž‰laęž‰ nowoęž‰ asuloęž‰ imilig dowaki, towoęž‰ dinali saetalega, dinali saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ imilig nomaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰waęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰ib, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to nowoęž‰ moęž‰baęž‰maęž‰ib. Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ dinali saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 3.16 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 12.7\x*Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ dinali saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ Ablaham oęž‰liaęž‰ e maęž‰mu imilig oęž‰liaęž‰moęž‰ sioęž‰. Godeyaęž‰ bugoęž‰ aęž‰namiloęž‰ to saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ â€śe maęž‰mu iâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. â€śE maęž‰mu imiligâ€ť aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. E maęž‰mu imilig aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ Keliso aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ sioęž‰.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 3.17 \xt Kis 12.40\x*To niloęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰l wemaęž‰ haęž‰goęž‰ we. Tamin amioęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ Ablaham e oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ towoęž‰ dinali saefaęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ donayoęž‰ 430 aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ Moęž‰saęž‰sboęž‰woęž‰ eleyoęž‰ dimi. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ele aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Ablaham emoęž‰loęž‰ to saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰dilaki, dinali saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ mada moęž‰koęž‰loęž‰.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 3.18 \xt Lom 4.14\x*Nioęž‰ ele kudu haęž‰nab aęž‰nami Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ boba kelegoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na diaęž‰noęž‰ kiboęž‰bowoęž‰, nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰ moęž‰dimabe. Koęž‰sega Gode eyoęž‰ Ablaham e oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laki dinali saefaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, boba kelegoęž‰woęž‰ e aęž‰na di.   
\p
\v 19 \x - \xo 3.19 \xt Ilig 7.38, Lom 5.20\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Moęž‰saęž‰s emoęž‰loęž‰ ele dimi aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰? Kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidakiloęž‰ hala haęž‰naęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ kalaba walamaęž‰ki, ele aęž‰noęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ gasalifaęž‰. Ele aęž‰noęž‰ dowaęž‰i yaęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰, Ablahamaęž‰ e maęž‰mu imilig, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ tamin amiloęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowabiki edoęž‰. Ele aęž‰noęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalumoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ us kalu Moęž‰saęž‰s emoęž‰ dimi, koęž‰loęž‰ Moęž‰saęž‰s e Godeyoęž‰ nol, kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ nol, aęž‰loęž‰ usa elen.  
\v 20 Usamiloęž‰ dowab kalu aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, kalu aęž‰laęž‰ usa dowakiloęž‰ asuwaęž‰tanoęž‰ oęž‰m. Koęž‰sega Godeyoęž‰ imilise e koęž‰loęž‰, eyoęž‰ Ablahamboęž‰ dinali saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, ene ka sioęž‰. \fig Moęž‰saęž‰s eyoęž‰ ele aęž‰noęž‰ uwa saęž‰saęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ diaęž‰mioęž‰.|alt="Moses with stone tablets" src="02_Ex_35_02_RG_gr.tif" size="col" copy="Â© Sweet Publishing http://sweetpublishing.com, licensed under a CC: BY-SA 3.0 Unported licence." ref="3.19" \fig*   
\p
\v 21 \x - \xo 3.21 \xt Lom 8.2-4\x*Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ele difaęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gisoęž‰ dowabaęž‰le? A aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰gab. Ele difaęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰ngoęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰le dimian kibabeyoęž‰, kaluwoęž‰ ele kudu haęž‰nab aęž‰namioęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ e digaloęž‰ kalu dowab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ oęž‰li saęž‰mabe.  
\v 22 Koęž‰sega Godeyaęž‰ to saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰, â€śHenfeloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale tambowoęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰ga iliki, dibolowa disaęž‰foęž‰len.â€ť Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ tamin amiloęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ tilidabu enedoęž‰ aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, oęž‰li diaęž‰ib.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 3.23 \xt Gala 4.3\x*Keliso e amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰baęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ kalab amioęž‰ oęž‰faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰namioęž‰, ele aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ melaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ dibolowa toęž‰lo alifoęž‰len.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 3.24 \xt Lom 10.4\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Keliso e oęž‰miaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰labikiyoęž‰, ele aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰len. Nioęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ digaloęž‰ kalu domaęž‰kiyoęž‰, ele aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ tililiaęž‰gaęž‰ Yaęž‰suloęž‰wa taęž‰foęž‰.  
\v 25 Oęž‰goęž‰ tilidabu man aęž‰noęž‰ mioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ eleyaęž‰ haęž‰g amioęž‰ moęž‰domaęž‰noęž‰. Ele aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ moęž‰boęž‰foęž‰melaęž‰ib.   
\s1 Nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene soęž‰wale dowab  
\p
\v 26 \x - \xo 3.26 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.12\x*Gioęž‰ tambo Yaęž‰su Kelisowa tilidabu koęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene soęž‰wale dowab.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 3.27 \xt Lom 6.3\x*Gioęž‰ hoęž‰n ami toęž‰lolabikiloęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowa dowab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, Kelisowaęž‰ helebesoęž‰g hoęž‰gi oęž‰ngoęž‰maęž‰ momade alifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 3.28 \xt Lom 10.12\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso amiloęž‰ dowoęž‰ gi aęž‰noęž‰, tambowoęž‰ imilise koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab. Yu kalu oęž‰liaęž‰ Gilig kalu oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ imilig dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Daęž‰iboęž‰ kaluwoęž‰loęž‰, gaęž‰liloęž‰ sab kaluwoęž‰loęž‰ imilig dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Kaluwoęž‰loęž‰, gayoęž‰loęž‰ imilig dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 3.29 \xt Lom 4.13\x*Kelisowaęž‰ enoęž‰le dowab gioęž‰, Ablahamaęž‰ ene soęž‰wale dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ gioęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰ib.   
\c 4  
\p
\v 1 Gioęž‰ fanda asulumaęž‰kiyoęž‰, niyoęž‰ towoęž‰ daęž‰fe saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. Soęž‰wa waęž‰laęž‰b aęž‰noęž‰ iyayoęž‰ sowalikiyoęž‰, hen oęž‰liaęž‰ dabun oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ e diaęž‰ib. Koęž‰sega e soęž‰walaęž‰su elen ami iyayoęž‰ aęž‰na sowalega, e hendele hendoęž‰ bisoęž‰ domaęž‰ib. Koęž‰sega kelegoęž‰ eloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ nolbaęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰liki e madali nanog dian kalu oęž‰ngoęž‰ elen.  
\v 2 Soęž‰wa aęž‰maęž‰loęž‰ kelegoęž‰ tamboloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ iyayaęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, hoęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰semoęž‰faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, soęž‰wa aęž‰noęž‰ eloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lab kalu aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰ga melaęž‰ib.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 4.3 \xt Kolo 2.20\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nioęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ elen. Tamin amioęž‰ nioęž‰ soęž‰wa oęž‰ngoęž‰ ilikiyoęž‰, henfeloęž‰ wenamiloęž‰ mama koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰waęž‰ halaidoęž‰ haęž‰ga siliki, madali nanog dian kalu oęž‰ngoęž‰ elen.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 4.4 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.14, Lom 1.3\x*Koęž‰sega hoęž‰lendeyoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowabikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ ene soęž‰wayoęž‰ iligaęž‰foęž‰. E gayaęž‰yoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰liaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Yuwaęž‰ ele difaęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰ga elen.  
\v 5 Nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene Soęž‰wale domaęž‰kiyoęž‰, ene soęž‰wayoęž‰ yaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, nioęž‰ ele haęž‰ga sen aęž‰noęž‰ gaęž‰li meseaęž‰ki, e aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ kililiaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 4.6 \xt Lom 8.15-17\x*Oęž‰goęž‰ nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene soęž‰wale dowoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ widakiyoęž‰, eyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ ene Mamayoęž‰ ni asuloęž‰ usa meleaęž‰ki iligaęž‰foęž‰. Mama aęž‰noęž‰ ni oęž‰liaęž‰ silikiyoęž‰ â€śDo, Do,â€ť aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ hoęž‰le saęž‰laęž‰lab.  
\v 7 Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰ gioęž‰ ele haęž‰ga iliki madali nanog dian kaluwoęž‰ moęž‰dowaki, Godeyaęž‰ ene soęž‰wale dowab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ soęž‰wale dowab gi aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, iyayaęž‰ dabun kelegoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ hendele diaęž‰ib.   
\s1 Galasia kaluwoęž‰ towoęž‰ kudu hoęž‰noęž‰babese aęž‰laęž‰asulaki sioęž‰  
\p
\v 8 Tamin amioęž‰ gioęž‰ Godeloęž‰ moęž‰fanda asuloęž‰ amioęž‰, madali gode koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰ga iliki, ini madali nanog dian kalu dofoęž‰len. I aęž‰noęž‰ gode hendelema.  
\v 9 Koęž‰sega oęž‰goęž‰ gioęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ fanda baęž‰daki asulab. Koęž‰sega oęž‰ngoęž‰ma. Hendele, Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ fanda baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ asuloęž‰. Mama koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wenamiloęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ halaidoęž‰loęž‰ma dowab koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ aęž‰na aęž‰kudu haęž‰nab ko waga dimidaya? Gioęž‰ ene madali nanog dian kalu aęž‰domaęž‰noęž‰ asulaya?  
\v 10 \x - \xo 4.10 \xt Lom 14.5, Kolo 2.16\x*Gililoęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰senoęž‰ we. Giliyoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ sagalemaęž‰ki, hoęž‰len alan nol ami gulugululakiyoęž‰, imo aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, taęž‰n aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ dona hoęž‰gi faęž‰laęž‰dowab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ duludaki gulugululaęž‰sen.  
\v 11 Gililoęž‰ dimidaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ ne daęž‰daęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, nanog niloęž‰, giloęž‰ amiloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ madali walab aęž‰laęž‰asulakiyoęž‰, ne kele asuloęž‰woęž‰ alan dowoęž‰.   
\p
\v 12 Wai! Nao nado i, ne giloęž‰wa mioęž‰ amioęž‰, Yuwaęž‰ eleyoęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, gi oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ gioęž‰loęž‰ ne dowoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ domaęž‰ki asuloęž‰l. Giliyoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ nowoęž‰ nemoęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰dimidale.  
\v 13 Gioęž‰ aęž‰asuluma. Tamin amioęž‰ ne walaf delen koęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰ ne giloęž‰wa yaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ to nafayoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na widoęž‰.  
\v 14 Ni doęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ halaidoęž‰loęž‰ma dowoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ dimi koęž‰sega, giliyoęž‰ ne dianilakiyoęž‰ moęž‰gola baęž‰baęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰ba. Godeyaęž‰ ene maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalu koęž‰loęž‰ tilidomaęž‰ib oęž‰leaumboęž‰, giliyoęž‰ ne aęž‰laęž‰tili dowoęž‰. Hendele gililoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso tilidomaęž‰ib oęž‰leaumboęž‰loęž‰, ne aęž‰laęž‰tili dowoęž‰.  
\v 15 Hoęž‰len aęž‰namiloęž‰ sagaloęž‰ giloęž‰ amiloęž‰ elen aęž‰noęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ oęž‰ba aneyoęž‰? Hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰ giliyoęž‰ oęž‰li dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ kiboęž‰bowoęž‰, goęž‰noęž‰n si ko duguliaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰li dimibabe. Niyoęž‰ mada hende aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰.  
\v 16 Koęž‰sega niloęž‰ gimoęž‰loęž‰ to hendele widoęž‰l wena ilikiyoęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ giliyoęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰beaki, gis dowabaęž‰le?   
\p
\v 17 Widan kalu i wemaęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ ililoęž‰ asulab au kudu menaęž‰ki, nanogoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dimidaki haęž‰nolaęž‰lab. Koęž‰sega ililoęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ gioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asuwaęž‰faęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki gaęž‰laba. Gioęž‰ ne oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ miliyoęž‰ moęž‰domaęž‰ki kaęž‰laki susudab koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ ililoęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ kudu hamanaęž‰ki gab.  
\v 18 Ne gi oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰lalikiyoęž‰loęž‰, neloęž‰malamioęž‰loęž‰, kalu nomaęž‰yoęž‰ man nafale dimidaki, gioęž‰ halale tili domaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laki dimidalega, man aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰li nafaleyoęž‰ koęž‰m.   
\p
\v 19 Ni soęž‰wa gioęž‰, gayaęž‰loęž‰ soęž‰wa saęž‰laęž‰liaęž‰nikiloęž‰ nagaloęž‰ dian aumboęž‰, neloęž‰ gi asulakiyoęž‰ nagaloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ dioęž‰l. Nagaloęž‰ us wenamioęž‰ halaidoęž‰ diaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰, gioęž‰ Keliso amioęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dowaliki taęž‰faęž‰noęž‰.  
\v 20 Ne gi oęž‰liaęž‰ mesaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ mada alan asuloęž‰l. Ne gi oęž‰liaęž‰ kona siliki kiboęž‰bowoęž‰, gi asuwaęž‰faęž‰noęž‰ togoęž‰ oęž‰li alobana soęž‰moęž‰lo. Koęž‰sega ne koęž‰naęž‰ siliki koęž‰loęž‰ kele asulaki babalab.   
\s1 Haęž‰ga oęž‰liaęž‰ Saęž‰la oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ soęž‰wa  
\p
\v 21 Kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ Moęž‰saęž‰saęž‰ ele aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰ asulab koęž‰loęž‰, kalu gi ko Moęž‰saęž‰saęž‰ eleyaęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ gioęž‰ fanda asululiyaęž‰le?  
\v 22 \x - \xo 4.22 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 16.15, 21.2\x*Godeyaęž‰ bugoęž‰ amioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. Ablaham eyoęž‰ kalu soęž‰wayoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰li. Soęž‰wa nowoęž‰ madali nanogdoęž‰ dian gayaęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰li. Soęž‰wa nowoęž‰ ga gaęž‰liloęž‰ elen aęž‰maęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰li.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 4.23 \xt Lom 9.7-9\x*Madali nanogdoęž‰ dian gayaęž‰loęž‰ soęž‰wa saęž‰laęž‰li aęž‰noęž‰ kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ asulab man aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰li. Koęž‰sega gaęž‰liloęž‰ elen ga aęž‰maęž‰loęž‰ soęž‰wa saęž‰laęž‰li aęž‰noęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ enedoęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ ilili alitaki saęž‰laęž‰li.  
\v 24 Ga aęž‰laęž‰ wenamiloęž‰ bale soęž‰loęž‰l aęž‰noęž‰ we. Ga aęž‰laęž‰ wenamioęž‰, nioęž‰ Gode oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ ege domaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰likiloęž‰ tog aęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ bale sioęž‰. Ga nowoęž‰ ene wiyoęž‰ Haęž‰ga. Sainai misioęž‰ amioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene eleyoęž‰ aęž‰na saefaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, Haęž‰ga e Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰namiloęž‰ saefaęž‰yoęž‰ oęž‰m. Ga aęž‰maęž‰loęž‰ soęž‰wa saęž‰laęž‰liab aęž‰noęž‰ madali nanog dian kalu taęž‰faęž‰ib.  
\v 25 Haęž‰ga e Alabia hen amiloęž‰ Sainai misioęž‰ oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ kaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki bale sioęž‰. Haęž‰ga oęž‰liaęž‰ ene soęž‰wa saęž‰laęž‰li aęž‰noęž‰ madali nanog dian kalukaęž‰isale dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ oęž‰gdoęž‰ Yaęž‰lusalemdoęž‰ sab kalukaęž‰isale iyoęž‰ eleyoęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, Haęž‰ga oęž‰ngoęž‰ ka dowaki, iyoęž‰loęž‰ madali nanog dian kalukaęž‰isale faęž‰laęž‰dowab.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 4.26 \xt Hibu 12.22, Kala 21.2,10\x*Koęž‰sega akin halonamiloęž‰ Yaęž‰lusalem hoęž‰gi aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ Saęž‰la oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowab. Yaęž‰lusalem aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰ Saęž‰la oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gaęž‰li sen koęž‰loęž‰, Saęž‰la e Keliso kalukaęž‰isale nili noęž‰le koęž‰loęž‰ dowab.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 4.27 \xt Ais 54.1\x*Aisaya bugoęž‰ amioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰lab.  
\q1 â€śFaino dowoęž‰ ga ge sagalema.  
\q2 Soęž‰wa saęž‰laęž‰liakiloęž‰ nagaloęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰di ge, guloęž‰ gulaki, sagalaęž‰li hoęž‰lema.  
\q1 Ga inaęž‰loęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰ ge, soęž‰wayoęž‰ modoęž‰le saęž‰laęž‰lakiyoęž‰, ga indoęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ gi tininilaęž‰maęž‰ib.â€ť   
\m
\v 28 \x - \xo 4.28 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 15.4-5, Lom 9.7\x*Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ amiloęž‰ Aisaęž‰g saęž‰laęž‰li oęž‰leaumboęž‰, gioęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰ ene soęž‰wale faęž‰laęž‰dowab.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 4.29 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 21.9-10, Yoęž‰n 8.35\x*Tamin amioęž‰ kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ asulab man aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ soęž‰wa saęž‰laęž‰li aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, Mamayaęž‰ halaidoęž‰ aęž‰na ilikiloęž‰ soęž‰wa saęž‰laęž‰li oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ dimiaęž‰len. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ oęž‰g wenamioęž‰loęž‰ man oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ka dimidaki, eleloęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen kalu iliyoęž‰, nimoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ dimiaęž‰lab.   
\p
\v 30 Koęž‰sega Godeyaęž‰ bugoęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰lab. â€śGaęž‰liloęž‰ sab gayaęž‰ soęž‰wa aęž‰noęž‰, madali nanog dian gayaęž‰ insoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ dabunoęž‰ mada moęž‰alobaęž‰maęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, giyoęž‰ madali nanog dian ga oęž‰liaęž‰ ene insoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ taęž‰taki, oęž‰lugaęž‰foma.â€ť  
\v 31 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ni nao nado i, nioęž‰ madali nanogdoęž‰ dian gayaęž‰ soęž‰wama. Nioęž‰ gaęž‰liloęž‰ sen ga aęž‰maęž‰ ene soęž‰wale koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab.   
\c 5  
\s1 Keliso eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ gaęž‰li meseaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab  
\p
\v 1 Keliso eyoęž‰ nanogoęž‰ diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, nioęž‰ gaęž‰li meseaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ mada halale kagayaki, ele kudu haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ waęž‰ka mele alitaki, madali nanog dian kalu oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowabenaęž‰ki, dinafa dowaęž‰bi.   
\p
\v 2 Ne Foęž‰l, niyoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ fanda saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l koęž‰loęž‰, to we dinafa dabuma! Giliyoęž‰ â€śne doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedeab aęž‰namioęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ ne digaloęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰ib,â€ť aęž‰laęž‰asulaki gedealega, Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ nanog di aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰maloęž‰ngoęž‰ dowaki, ge moęž‰asuwaęž‰faęž‰ib.  
\v 3 To we niyoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ waęž‰ka halale aęž‰soęž‰loęž‰l. Kalu abeyoęž‰ doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedemaęž‰noęž‰ man koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰nab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, Yuwaęž‰ ele nol aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ tambowoęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰meleaęž‰ki gab.  
\v 4 Kalu abeyoęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ e digaloęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰baęž‰ki, Yuwaęž‰ ele aęž‰noęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lalega, e Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ elenoęž‰ gedegaęž‰tab koęž‰m. Eyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ dowoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ gola baęž‰dakigab.  
\v 5 Yaęž‰su amiloęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale nioęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ digaloęž‰ taęž‰fomaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Mamayaęž‰ halaidoęž‰wa iliki, tilidaęž‰daęž‰li yasisoęž‰l.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 5.6 \xt 1Kol 7.19, Gala 6.15\x*Keliso amiloęž‰ dowab gioęž‰, doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedeoęž‰waęž‰le, moęž‰gedeoęž‰waęž‰le, Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ma dowab. Yaęž‰su amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lakiloęž‰ dowab aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ alandeyoęž‰ oęž‰m.   
\p
\v 7 Gioęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, halale nai haęž‰naęž‰len koęž‰sega, gioęž‰ to hendeleloęž‰ moęž‰kudu ane aęž‰noęž‰ kalu abe aniliaęž‰ haęž‰nabeyoęž‰?  
\v 8 Asuloęž‰ gililoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ sendeliaęž‰ haęž‰nab aęž‰noęž‰, geloęž‰ hoęž‰leli Gode aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ mioęž‰ma.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 5.9 \xt 1Kol 5.6\x*Maęž‰n haloęž‰woęž‰ diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ maęž‰n nafa oęž‰liaęž‰ woęž‰gelalega, maęž‰n aęž‰noęž‰ tambo haloęž‰ domaęž‰ib. Ililoęž‰ to hala widab aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ dowab.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 5.10 \xt 2Kol 11.15, Gala 1.7\x*Koęž‰sega nioęž‰ Yaęž‰suwa ogaęž‰di dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ tog no amioęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naki, to niloęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰tili asuloęž‰l. Kalu abeyoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ towoęž‰ hala widaki, gili asuloęž‰woęž‰ yoęž‰le alitab aęž‰noęž‰, e waęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰ib.  
\v 11 Ni nao nado i, niyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedema aęž‰laęž‰liki widaęž‰li kiboęž‰bowoęž‰, iliyoęž‰ nagaloęž‰ we nemoęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰dimibabe. Niyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso koęž‰loęž‰ i malan amiloęž‰ sowoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰widaęž‰li kiboęž‰bowoęž‰, ili asuloęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰kulufaęž‰mabe.  
\v 12 Kalu gili asuloęž‰loęž‰ noęž‰noloęž‰ alitab aęž‰noęž‰, ininoęž‰ doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedeakiyoęž‰, usoęž‰loęž‰ tambo dugulalega, niyoęž‰ oęž‰li aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰l.   
\p
\v 13 \x - \xo 5.13 \xt 1Bid 2.16\x*Nao nado i, Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ gaęž‰li meseaęž‰ki daęž‰feaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ ele haęž‰g amioęž‰ moęž‰dowab. Koęž‰sega gioęž‰ gaęž‰li dowoęž‰l aęž‰laęž‰asulakiyoęž‰, goęž‰noęž‰n doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ asulab aęž‰noęž‰ kudu haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, mogagoęž‰woęž‰ dimidaęž‰soęž‰bo. Aęž‰laęž‰ba. Giliyoęž‰ nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lakiyoęž‰ asuwaęž‰taęž‰lubi.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 5.14 \xt Wkp 19.18, Lom 13.9\x*Ele imilig wenamioęž‰, ele difaęž‰ noloęž‰ tambo kegeneliaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, us aęž‰na daęž‰lab. Ele alande aęž‰noęž‰ we â€śGioęž‰ goęž‰noęž‰n asulan oęž‰leaumboęž‰, giasi kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asulaki haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰bi.â€ť  
\v 15 Koęž‰sega gegeleboęž‰ nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ kegefoęž‰koęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰lalega, dinafa dowaęž‰bi! Giliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidalega, tilidabu gililoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ tambo mogagilaęž‰maęž‰ib.   
\s1 Mamayaęž‰loęž‰ asulab au kudu haęž‰naęž‰bi  
\p
\v 16 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ niyoęž‰ to we aęž‰laęž‰soęž‰loęž‰l. Mamayaęž‰ halaidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ tililiaęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰meleaęž‰ki taęž‰foma. Gioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidalega, doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ meselan man aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰dimidamaęž‰ib.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 5.17 \xt Lom 7.15-23\x*Doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ meselan man aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, Mama Maliloęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ asulab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ sana toęž‰lolaęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Mamayaęž‰loęž‰ asulab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ meselan man aęž‰noęž‰ sana toęž‰lolaęž‰lab. Gili asuloęž‰ usamioęž‰ man aęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ iliki, tadowoęž‰laki bubaęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰gab amioęž‰, giloęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ asulab aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ dowab.  
\v 18 Koęž‰sega gioęž‰ Mama maliloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ tililiaęž‰ hamanaęž‰ki taęž‰talega, ge ele aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰g amioęž‰ moęž‰dowab.   
\p
\v 19 \x - \xo 5.19 \xt 1Kol 6.9-10\x*Doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ meselan man aęž‰noęž‰, kalab amiloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowanoęž‰ we. Uwoęž‰ dianoęž‰, no oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ uwoęž‰ diaęž‰noęž‰ mada alan asulanoęž‰,  
\v 20 madali gode gulugululanoęž‰, fofa dimidanoęž‰, eteanoęž‰, mululoęž‰ to saęž‰lanoęž‰, kelegoęž‰ nomaęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰lab asulanoęž‰, gadianoęž‰, noęž‰noęž‰naęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ asulanoęž‰, soęž‰loęž‰woęž‰ alobaęž‰dakiloęž‰ inaęž‰li inaęž‰li aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dowanoęž‰,  
\v 21 meselanoęž‰, alunaęž‰ hoęž‰n nakiloęž‰ noęž‰nolanoęž‰, mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidamaęž‰nikiloęž‰ kegeaęž‰lab manoęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ mogagoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ nol aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ka dimidaęž‰labiki aęž‰na soęž‰loęž‰l. Niloęž‰ tamin amiloęž‰ hagugoęž‰ to sioęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ waęž‰ka aęž‰soęž‰loęž‰l. Kalukaęž‰isale man koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰melaęž‰nigab us aęž‰namioęž‰ moęž‰tinaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 22 Koęž‰sega Godeyaęž‰ Mamayaęž‰loęž‰ nioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ tili dowakiloęž‰ fo helemaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ we. Noloęž‰ mada alan asulanoęž‰, sagalanoęž‰, haęž‰sa dowanoęž‰, haęž‰faęž‰nolo dowanoęž‰, haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lanoęž‰, nolboęž‰woęž‰ man nafale dimidanoęž‰, halale tili asulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ dimidanoęž‰,  
\v 23 haęž‰nolo saęž‰lanoęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ goęž‰noęž‰naęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ dinafa tili dowanoęž‰. Gioęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰nalega, ge ele imilig noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰gumaęž‰ib.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 5.24 \xt Lom 6.6, Kolo 3.5\x*Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰noęž‰ dowoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, enedoęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ asulan aęž‰noęž‰ tambo i malana alu alitaki, sana sowoęž‰.   
\p
\v 25 Godeyaęž‰ Mama aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ nimoęž‰ dimi koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ Mama eloęž‰ asulab au kudu haęž‰naęž‰melaęž‰niki.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 5.26 \xt Fili 2.3\x*Nioęž‰ nininaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ oęž‰li aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ asulaęž‰soęž‰bo. Nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ babumaęž‰kiyoęž‰ digene meaęž‰soęž‰bo. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu nol oęž‰liaęž‰ eteakiyoęž‰ mululaęž‰soęž‰bo.   
\c 6  
\s1 Kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ asuwaęž‰taęž‰lubi  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 6.1 \xt Madi 18.15\x*Nao nado i, kalu imilig nowoęž‰ mogagoęž‰wa sulufoęž‰ tinalega, tilidabuwoęž‰ halaidoęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰aęž‰lab giliyoęž‰, kalu aęž‰noęž‰ haęž‰sa gasiliaki, digale alitaęž‰bi. Giliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ dimidakiyoęž‰, goęž‰noęž‰n geloęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰ sulufoęž‰ tinabenaęž‰ki, dinafa halale dowaęž‰bi.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 6.2 \xt Lom 15.1\x*Gioęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ diab amioęž‰, gegeleboęž‰ nowoęž‰ asuwaęž‰taęž‰bi. Man aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dimidab aęž‰namioęž‰, Kelisowaęž‰ ele saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ mada ilili alifaęž‰ib.  
\v 3 Kalu abeyoęž‰ e alan wiloęž‰kaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lab koęž‰sega, eloęž‰ to saęž‰lab oęž‰liaęž‰ man dimidan oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ imiloęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dowalega, enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ dikili saęž‰laki gab.  
\v 4 Nanog goęž‰noęž‰ndoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ goęž‰noęž‰noęž‰ dinafa alobana baęž‰daęž‰bi. Nanog goęž‰noęž‰ndoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ nafa baęž‰dalega, goęž‰noęž‰noęž‰ sagalaęž‰bi. Koęž‰sega nanog kalu nomaęž‰loęž‰ di aęž‰noęž‰, giloęž‰ di aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ daęž‰feakiyoęž‰, alobana baęž‰daęž‰soęž‰bo.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 6.5 \xt Lom 14.12\x*Kaluwoęž‰ tambo inaęž‰li inaęž‰liloęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ nanog di aęž‰noęž‰, enedoęž‰lekoęž‰ dinafa tilidowaka boęž‰foęž‰lubi.   
\p
\v 6 \x - \xo 6.6 \xt 1Kol 9.11,14\x*Tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale giliyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ nafale daęž‰labko, kalu gimoęž‰loęž‰ toloęž‰ widab oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ alobaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ dimiaęž‰bi.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 6.7 \xt Lom 8.13\x*Giliyoęž‰ gininaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ dikidaęž‰soęž‰bo. Godeyoęž‰ giliyoęž‰ mada moęž‰dikilimaęž‰ib. Giliyoęž‰ fo oęž‰boęž‰ngoęž‰waęž‰le egeloęž‰ amiloęž‰ gelab aęž‰noęž‰, aęž‰maęž‰ ene folekoęž‰ tumaęž‰ib.  
\v 8 Kalu abeyoęž‰ ene doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ meselan man aęž‰noęž‰ kudu haęž‰naki, man mogagoęž‰ dimidalega, fo hedan aumboęž‰ somaęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰ib. Kalu abeyoęž‰ Mamayaęž‰loęž‰ asulab au kudu haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, man nafale dimidalega, fo hedan aumboęž‰ Mama eya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰ngoęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ diaęž‰ib.  
\v 9 Aęž‰laęž‰maęž‰noęž‰loęž‰biki, nioęž‰ man nafa dimidaki, dinafa kudu haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, moęž‰moęž‰bemaęž‰niki. Nioęž‰ boęž‰sulakiyoęž‰ moęž‰taęž‰talega, hoęž‰lende aęž‰noęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, fo aęž‰noęž‰ nafale ililoęž‰ tumaęž‰noęž‰.  
\v 10 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ fogdoęž‰ dowab hoęž‰len wenamioęž‰, niliyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale tambomoęž‰woęž‰ man nafale dimidamaęž‰niki. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Keliso kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰lab oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ man nafale mada dimidamaęž‰niki.   
\s1 Melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ hoęž‰giloęž‰ diab aęž‰noęž‰ alandeyoęž‰ oęž‰m  
\p
\v 11 Moęž‰foęž‰s we edakiyoęž‰, noęž‰noęž‰n dagileyaęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ todaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ baęž‰dakiyoęž‰, ni dagiyaęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰asulaęž‰bi.  
\v 12 Kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ wi alan diaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asulakiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedemaęž‰ki halaidoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰lab. Yu kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ imoęž‰woęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ dimiabenaęž‰kiyoęž‰, iliyoęž‰ Keliso i malan amiloęž‰ sowoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰fanda widaki, doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedema aęž‰lakiyoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰lab.  
\v 13 Kalu aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ widab i aęž‰noęž‰ doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedeoęž‰ koęž‰sega, ele aęž‰noęž‰ tambowoęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen. Koęž‰sega iyoęž‰ wiyoęž‰ alan diaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰lakiyoęž‰, giyoęž‰loęž‰ doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedemaęž‰ki susiab. \fig Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ ene dagiyaęž‰yoęž‰ to noloęž‰ todaęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰.|alt="Paul with large handwriting" src="C103_gr.tif" size="col" copy="Â© 1997 New Tribes Mission/Foreign Mission Board, Southern Baptist Convention. Used with permission." ref="6.11" \fig*   
\p
\v 14 Koęž‰sega niyoęž‰ ne noęž‰noęž‰naęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ wi duludaki goęž‰ba. Alan Yaęž‰su Keliso koęž‰loęž‰ i malan amiloęž‰ sowoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ne duludaki saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰. Yaęž‰su i malan amiloęž‰ sana sowoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, ne amiloęž‰ henfeloęž‰waęž‰ man dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ asulan aęž‰noęž‰ sana sowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale henfeloęž‰ man weloęž‰ dimidab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ne oęž‰ngoęž‰maloęž‰ngoęž‰ baęž‰dab.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 6.15 \xt Gala 5.6, 2Kol 5.17\x*Kaluwoęž‰ doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedeoęž‰lalikiyoęž‰loęž‰, moęž‰hege gedeoęž‰lalikiyoęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰mal dowab. Koęž‰sega kaluwaęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰giloęž‰ diab aęž‰noęž‰ alandeyoęž‰ oęž‰m.  
\v 16 Gode eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale man weloęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab i oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ nofolo alitaki, haęž‰sa meseaęž‰ki taęž‰faęž‰ib. Kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyaęž‰noęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale hendeleyoęž‰ oęž‰m.   
\p
\v 17 \x - \xo 6.17 \xt 2Kol 4.10\x*Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalu i nol wemaęž‰yoęž‰ gili saęž‰soęž‰ alobaęž‰dakiyoęž‰, hidaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ waęž‰kabiyoęž‰ moęž‰diminaęž‰ki asuloęž‰l. Ni doęž‰moęž‰ amiloęž‰ imu woęž‰len wemaęž‰ saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, ne Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ ene nanog dian kalukaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki widakigab.  
\v 18 Ni nao nado i, nili Alan Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ ene haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ gi mama oęž‰liaęž‰ domaęž‰ki, niyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l. Hendele.   